# ARSession.CollaborationData.Priority.critical

**Case**

A priority that indicates that collaboration depends on this data.

## Declaration

```swift
case critical
```

## Discussion

ARKit sets the data [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARSession/CollaborationData/priority-swift.property] to  [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARSession/CollaborationData/Priority-swift.enum/critical]  when it’s needed to establish or continue a collaborative session.
